    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "今日も生徒会、忙しそう――\r\n……ですね、エアグルーヴ……先輩。",
            "enText": "I see the student council is busy as always. \nI hope you're faring well, Air— um, I mean \n<i>Ms.</i> Air Groove.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "pathId": -7040388902423105837,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "エアグルーヴ",
            "enName": "Air Groove",
            "jpText": "うっ……なんだ、その話し方は。\r\n据わりが悪い。",
            "enText": "…Why are you talking like that? \nIs something wrong?",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "voiceIdx": 1,
            "pathId": -4355224239718470334,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "スぺちゃんがね、敬語だから……\r\n私もそうした方がいいのかな、って。",
            "enText": "Spe is always so polite around you, \nso I thought I should do the same…",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "pathId": -7458679021894647113,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "エアグルーヴ",
            "enName": "Air Groove",
            "jpText": "そういうことか……まあ、私としては\r\n気軽に接してもらって構わんのだが。",
            "enText": "So that's it… Well, not that I mind \nformal language in general…",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "voiceIdx": 3,
            "pathId": -9208195547950606151,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "エアグルーヴ",
            "enName": "Air Groove",
            "jpText": "それに、我々は親しい友人だろう。\r\nなおのこと遠慮は無用だ。いつも通りでいい。",
            "enText": "But you and I are far too close for that, no? \nI see no point in keeping each other at \narm's length.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "voiceIdx": 4,
            "pathId": 3144296985240462988,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "……ふふっ、そうね。",
            "enText": "…Hehe, true.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "pathId": -8376601663854078159,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "友人であり……\r\nライバルのあなたに、遠慮はなし……ね。",
            "enText": "Then I won't hold back in \nmy speech… or our races.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "voiceIdx": 6,
            "pathId": -8533545218428674982,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "エアグルーヴ",
            "enName": "Air Groove",
            "jpText": "……！",
            "enText": "…!",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "voiceIdx": 7,
            "pathId": 6192559840744976203,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "エアグルーヴ",
            "enName": "Air Groove",
            "jpText": "……ふん、言ってくれる。",
            "enText": "…Heh, that's what I like to hear.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "voiceIdx": 8,
            "pathId": 1546772878117441836,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "ふふふっ。",
            "enText": "Ehehe.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "voiceIdx": 9,
            "pathId": -5243350520532550822,
            "blockIdx": 10
        }
    ],
